data.name: helpTextBox.Text
data.value:
Project Manager Help ------------------------------- * This application helps to manage all the solution files of C#. Though it may work even for Vb , this hasn't been tested yet.
* It can be used to manage more than 1 folder that contains the solutions
* The Major functionality of this app lies in the right click facility provided to it
* Projects can be added, removed and overwritten, or the selected project can be run or that project folder can be opened.
* The Size of the project manager can also be remembered using the right click functionality provided to the tray icon
--------------------------------------- Press any key to close this :) ---------------------------------------
